quran[98]{c,v,t}:
  19,1,"Kaaf Haa Yaa ayn saad."
  19,2,"JaЕ‹to Yurmeende Joomi maaЙ—a jeyaaЙ—o makko on Jakariyaa."
  19,3,"Tuma nde o noddunoo Joom makko noddaannu suuЙ—iindu."
  19,4,"O maaki: ""Jooma, min dey Жґi'e Й—en lo'ii e am hoore nden ranwi puri, mi laataaki non Й—awaaЙ—o ka toragol ma Jooma."
  19,5,"Min dey mi hulii lomtotooЙ“e Й“en Й“aawo am, cuddiiЙ—o am on laatike dimaro okkam immorde ka maaЙ—a Й“iЙ—Й—o."
  19,6,"O rona kam, o rona kadi e Й“eynguure Yaaquuba nde waЙ—aa mo Joomi weltoraaЙ—o."
  19,7,"Eeyma Jakariyaa Minen Min mbeltinirii ma suka innde makko ko Yahyaa Min mbЙ—anaani mo ko adii tokoraajo."
  19,8,"O maaki: ""Jooma ko honno laatoranta kam suka sonnaajo am on laatike dimaro min kadi mi yottike e nayewu yooruЙ—o tere?"""
  19,9,"[Maleka on] wi'i: ""Ko nii Joomi maaЙ—a Daaliri: ЖЉum no neewii e Am gooЙ—ii Mi Tagiino ma ko adii, hari a laataaki huunde""."
  19,10,"O maaki: ""Jooma waЙ—anam ma'ande"". O Daali: ""ma'ande maaЙ—a nden ko wota a wowlidu e yimЙ“e Й“en jemmaaji tati potondirЙ—i""."
  19,11,"O yalti hakkunde yimЙ“e makko Й“en immorde ka ganngunal o joopii fa'ande e maЙ“Й“e, Й—um woni subunhinee bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e."
  19,12,"Eeyma Yahyaa nanngir deftere nden doole, min n ngokki mo Г±eeГ±al ko o suka."
  19,13,"E Yurmeende immorde ka amen ko o laaЙ“uЙ—o o laatike kuloowo [Alla]."
  19,14,"Ko o Й—igganЙ—o jipnaaЙ“e mo Й“en o wonaani ndunndarankeejo gaaЖґiiЙ—o."
  19,15,"Kisal e makko Г±ande o jibinaa e Г±ande o maayata e Г‘ande o immintintee ko o guuruЙ—o."
  19,16,"JaЕ‹to ka deftere Mariyama tuma nde o woЙ—Й—itinoo immorde e yimЙ“e makko Й“en [o yaari] e nokkuure funnaangeyaЕ‹koore."
  19,17,"O jogitii ga maЙ“Й“e wirngallo, min Nuli e makko Ruuhu amen o nanndintinanii mo e Й“anndiЕ‹ke fotondirЙ—o."
  19,18,"O maaki: min mi moolorii jurmoteeЙ—o On immorde e maaЙ—a si tawii a laatike ko a kulЙ—o [Alla]."
  19,19,"O wi'i: ""Pellet, min ko mi NulaaЙ—o Joomi maaЙ—a fii yo mi okke suka laaЙ“Й—o."
  19,20,"O wi'i: ""Ko hono laatoranta kam suka hara Й“anndiЕ‹ke memaani kam mi laataaki kadi jeenoowo(pijoowo)""."
  19,21,"O wi'i: ""ko nii Joomi maaЙ—a Daaliri: ""ЖЉuum no newii e am e fii yo min mbaЙ— mo ma'ande fii yimЙ“e Й“en e Yurmeende immornde e amen Й—um laatike fiyaake Г‘aawaaЙ—o""."
  19,22,"O roondii mo, o pottidodi e makko e nokkuure woЙ—Й—itiinde."
  19,23,"ЕЉata(qatwere) on fiЙ—i mo e jullere tamarohi, o wi'i: ""Ee hara noon mi maayno ko adii Й—um mi laatoo hu'unde yejjitaande""."
  19,24,"O noddi mo immorde e ley makki, [o wi'i] wota a suno gooЕ‹Й—ii Joomi maaЙ—a waЙ—ii ley maaЙ—a caatngol."
  19,25,"YeЖґu(dimmbu) fa'ade e maaЙ—a jullere tamarohi kin nde liЙ“a e ma,aЙ—a Й“ennduЙ—e teЙ“eteeЙ—e."
  19,26,"Г‘aam yaraa Й“uЙ“Й“inaa gite, si a yi'ii goЙ—Й—o immorde e Й“anndiЕ‹ke wi'u: ""Miin dey mi takkanii Hinnorante(jurmotooЙ—o korka mi wowlidata e neЙ—Й—aЕ‹ke hannde""."
  19,27,"O radi e makko ka yimЙ“e makko, homo tammbii mo Й“e wi'i: ""Ko an yo Mariyama gooЕ‹Й—ii a addii hu'unde hawnii nde""."
  19,28,"Eyma banndiraawo Haaruuna baaba maa laatanooki neЙ—Й—o bonЙ—o neene maaЙ—a kadi laataaki jinoowo."
  19,29,"[Mariyama] joopii e makko, Й“e mbi'i:""Ko hono min njewtirta e on sanfaajo gonЙ—o e woofordu(liir) gondo e tiiggu""."
  19,30,"[Iisaa] maaki: ""Miin dey ko mi jiyaaЙ—o Alla o okkii kam deftere nden o waЙ—ii kam annabaajo""."
  19,31,"O waЙ—i kam BarkinaaЙ—o nokku kala ka mi woni, o wasiyii kam Juulde nden e Jakka on fodde miЙ—o wuuri."
  19,32,"Ko mi Й—igganЙ—o yumma am, o waЙ—aani kam ndunndarankeejo malkisaaЙ—o."
  19,33,"Kisal on wonii e am Г±ande mi jibinaa e Г±ande mi maayata e Г±ande mi immintintee ko mi guuruЙ—o."
  19,34,"On ko Iisaa geЙ—al Mariyama Daalol Goongawol ngol heЙ“e cikkitoo fii mu'um."
  19,35,"Haananaa Alla nde o jogitotoo Й“iЙ—Й—o senaare e wonanii mo, si O Г±aawii fiyaake o daalanay mo tan: ""Won"" o wona."
  19,36,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon, mdewee o. Ko Й—um woni Laawol poocciingol""."
  19,37,"Pelle Й—e luutondiri hakkunde majji, bone wonanii Й“en yedduЙ“e ceedagol Г±alaande mawnde."
  19,38,"Kaawee ko nanirta yi'ira wa maЙ“Й“e Г‘ande Й“e aroyta e amen, kono tooГ±ooЙ“e Й“en hannde heЙ“e e ndeer majjere Й“anngunde."
  19,39,"KulЙ“inir Й“e Г±ande Nimse, tuma nde fiyaake on Г±aawaa hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e e ndeer welsindaare hara Й“e gooЕ‹Й—inaa."
  19,40,"Minen min ndonat lesdi ndi e Й“en wonЙ“e e dow mayri, ko ka amen Й“e nduttetee."
  19,41,"JaЕ‹to ka deftere Ibraahiima, pellet, kaЕ‹ko o laatino GoonguЙ—o annabaajo."
  19,42,"Tuma nde o maakannoo bem makko: ""eeyma baaba ko holЙ—um ndewantaa Й—um ko nanataa yi'ataa hara duncantaa ma hay e hu'unde?"
  19,43,"Eeyma baaba min dey gooЙ—ii arii am immorde e Ganndal kon ko araani e maaЙ—a, jokkam mi fewne e Laawol po'occiingol."
  19,44,"Eeyma baaba, wota a rew Seytaane, pellet, Seytaane laatike jedduЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o."
  19,45,"Eeyma baaba, min dey miЙ—o huli wota meeme Lepte immorde ka jurmotooЙ—o laatanoЙ—aa Seytaane giЙ—o."
  19,46,"[Baaba makko] wi'i: ""Enee, an a aГ± deweteeЙ—i am Й—in nee Ibraahiima, pellet, si a accaani mi fiЙ—ete selam dummunne [juutuЙ—o]."
  19,47,"[Ibraahiima] maaki: ""Kisal e maaЙ—a aray mi inminanomaa ka Joomi am, pellet, KoЕ‹ko O Laatike NewaniiЙ—o kam."
  19,48,"Mi martoo(deestoo) on e kon ko ndewoton ga Alla, mi toroo Joomi am no gasa mi wonataa tampirЙ—o toragol Joomi am."
  19,49,"Tuma nde o martinoo(deestinoo) Й“e e ko Й“e ndewata kon gaAlla, min n ngokki mo Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba kala [gooto e maЙ“Й“e] Men waЙ—i [mo] Annabaajo."
  19,50,"Min ngokki Й“e immorde e Yurmeende amen, min mbaЙ—ani Й“e mantoore toownde."
  19,51,"JaЕ‹to ka deftere Muusaa, pellet, kaЕ‹ko o laatinoke laЙ“Й“inЙ—o o laatinoke kadi NulaaЙ—o Annabiijo."
  19,52,"Min noddi mo ka senЕ‹go Г±aamo [fello] Tuuri Min Й“attini mo gunndeteeЙ—o."
  19,53,"Min ngokki mo immorde e Yurmeende amen musiЙ—Й—o makko on Haaruuna Annabiijo."
  19,54,"JaЕ‹to ka defftere Ismaa'iila, pellet, kaЕ‹ko o laatinoke gooЕ‹Й—uЙ—o fodoore o laatinoke kadi NulaaЙ—o Annabiijo."
  19,55,"O laatino himo yamira yimЙ“e makko Й“en Juulde e askal on, o laatino kadi beltoraaЙ—o ka Joomi makko."
  19,56,"JaЕ‹to ka deftere Idriisa, pellet, kaЕ‹ko o laatino goonguЙ—o Annabiijo."
  19,57,"Men Й“amti mo e nokkuure Toownde."
  19,58,"Ko Й“een ngoni Й“een, Й“e Alla Neemini e dow mu'en immorde e AnnabaaЙ“e ka geЙ—al Й“ebibbe Aadama e Й“en Й“e Men mbaЙ—Й—innoo wond'ude e Nuuhu e geЙ—alЙ“e Ibraahiima e Israa'iila e Й“en Й“e Min peewni min n cuЙ“ii si janngaama e dow maЙ“Й“e aayeeje Hinnorante Й“e fukko koЙ“e sujjooЙ“e e wullooЙ“e."
  19,59,"Lomtii Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e lomtotooЙ“e, Й“e njeeebi Juulde nden Й“e njokki welamuuji Й—in aray Й“e kawroya e bone."
  19,60,"Si wonaa on tuubuЙ—o o gooЕ‹Й—ini o golli ko moЖґЖґi, Й“en Й—on Й“e naatat Aljanna on Й“e tooГ±iroy- taake hay e huunde."
  19,61,"Aljannaaji Adan Й—in Й—i jurmotooЙ—o o Fodi jeyaaЙ“e makko Й“en e birnagal, pellet KaЕ‹ko, Fodoore Makko nden laatike ko aroore."
  19,62,"ЖЃe nanataa ndeer ton rayrayti si wonaa kisal no woodani Й“e arsike maЙ“Й“e on nder ton bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e."
  19,63,"Oon Aljanna mo Men ndoninta immorde e jeyaaЙ“e amen Й“en, on laatiiЙ—o kulol [Alla]."
  19,64,"Min njippotaako si wonaa e Yamaruyee Joomi maaЙ—a, no woodani mo ko woni kon hedde yeeso amen e ko woni kon Й“aawo amen e ko woni kon hakkunde Й—um, Joomi maaЙ—a laataaki yejjitoowo."
  19,65,"Jooma kammuuli Й—in e lesdi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, rew mo monГ±itor dewal makko. Taw si haЙ—a anndani mo tokoraajo?"
  19,66,"NeЙ—Й—aЕ‹ke on no wi'a: ""Eyoo, e jaka si mi maai aroyay ka mi yaltinee tawa ko mi guurЙ—o?"""
  19,67,"Enee, neЙ—Й—aЕ‹ke on annditaani Menen Men Tagiino mo ko adii, hari o wonaali hay e hu'unde."
  19,68,"Mi woondirii Joomi maaЙ—a min mooЙ“at Й“e sanne e Seytanuuji Й—in, refti min ngadda Й“e sara Jahannama ko Й“e jiccii Й“e."
  19,69,"Refti min n Й—o'ofa immorde e kala fedde ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e Й“urnoo saЙ—tude dartagol e dow jurmotooЙ—o e o."
  19,70,"Refti ko minen nganndi Й“een Й“urЙ“e haan'dude e sumugol e magge."
  19,71,"Alaa hay e gooto e mo'on si wanaa o joloyat e magge, Й—um laatike e dow Joomi maaЙ—a ko Г±aawaЙ—um TeeЕ‹tinaa."
  19,72,"Refti min ndaЙ—na Й“en hulunooЙ“e [Alla] min n Й—ala tooГ±ooЙ“e Й“en ko Й“e jicciiЙ“e ndeer ton."
  19,73,"Si janngaama e taweede maЙ“Й“e aayeeje amen ЖЃannguЙ—e Й—e yedduЙ“e Й“e mb'a gom- Й—imЙ“e Й“en: ""Ko honnde e feddeeji Й—i Й—iЙ—i Й“uri moЖґЖґude darnde Й“uri moЖґЖґude kadi batu""."
  19,74,"Heewii ko min kalki ado maЙ“Й“e immorde e gire tawi ko kamЙ“e Й“uri fotude mirannji suudu e mba'adi."
  19,75,"Maaku: ""On laatiiЙ—o e ndeer majjere nde yo jurmotooЙ—o fortan mo fontudee, haa si Й“e yi'ii ko Й“e fodaa kon, si tawii ko lepte Й—en maa si ko Darngal ngal, aray Й“e annda on m bonuЙ—o nukkuure e Й“urЙ—o lo'ude konu""."
  19,76,"Alla no Й“eydana Й“en feewЙ“e Peewal, MoЖґЖґi heddotooЙ—i Й—in Й“uri moЖґЖґude mbarjaari ka Joomi maaЙ—a Й“uri moЖґЖґude kadi ruttorde."
  19,77,"Enee, a yi'ii on jedduЙ—o aayeeje amen Й—e, o wi'i: ""Maatun mi okkee jawdi e Й“iЙ—Й—o""."
  19,78,"Enee o Жґelliti e ko wirnii kon, kaa jogiti ka jurmotooЙ—o e Aadi?"
  19,79,"Wonaa non, aray Min mbinnda ko o wi'ata kon min Й“eydana mo immorde e Lepte Й—en Й“eydude."
  19,80,"Min ndonna mo e ko o wi'ata ko, o ara e Amen ko o weddiiЙ—o(gooto)."
  19,81,"ЖЃe njogitii ga Alla deweteeЙ—i fii yo Й—i laatano Й“e semmbe."
  19,82,"Wonaa non, maЙ“e njeddu dewugolЙ“e ngol, Й“e laatanoo Й“e aГ±Й“e."
  19,83,"Enee a yiaani minen min Nulii Seytanuuji e dow yedduЙ“e Й“en hiЙ—i Жґuuna Й“e Жґuunudee."
  19,84,"Wata a hawjan Й“e, pellat, limonayЙ“ebe kala limugol."
  19,85,"Г‘ande Min mooЙ“oyta hulooЙ“e [Alla] Й“e ka jurmotooЙ—o TeddinaaЙ“e."
  19,86,"Men cogga bonЙ“e Й“e haa ka Jahannama ko Й“e jolooЙ“e."
  19,87,"ЖЃe maraa tefoore nden si wonaa on jogitiiЙ—o ka jurmotooЙ—o Aadi."
  19,88,"ЖЃe mbi'i: ""jurmotooЙ—o jogitike Й“iЙ—Й—o""."
  19,89,"GooЕ‹Й—ii on mgaddii hu'unde pankarЙ—ii nde."
  19,90,"Kammuuli Й—in no do'a(Й—esa) se'ekaade immorde e Й—uum leydi ndin feera pelle Й—e nduuya fii unagol."
  19,91,"fii Й“e noddanii jurmotooЙ—o Й“iЙ—Й—o."
  19,92,"Haananaa jurmotooЙ—o de o jogitotoo Й“iЙ—Й—o."
  19,93,"Alaa ko woni e kammuuli e leydi si wanaa o aray e jurmotooЙ—o hombo woni jeyaaЙ—o."
  19,94,"GooЙ—ii o moftii Й“e o limii Й“e kadi e limugol."
  19,95,"[Gooto] Kala e maЙ“Й“e aray Mo Г‘ande Darngako o woddiiЙ—o(teeldЙ—o)."
  19,96,"Pellet, Й“een gooЙ—inЙ“e ngolli ko moЖґЖґi ko aray ka jurmotooЙ—o waЙ—anaЙ“e Giggol."
  19,97,"Anndu ko min n newiniri nde ka Й—enngal maaЙ—a; ko fii yo a weltinir nde hulooЙ“e [Alla] Й“en njertiniraa nde yimЙ“e saЙ—tuЙ“e weeГ±re."
  19,98,"Heewii ko min kalki ado maЙ“Й“e e gire taw si hiЙ—a so'a e maЙ“Й“e immorde e goЙ—Й—o, maa haЙ—a nana Й“e hito?"
